### Place Order (Customer)
### Creates a new order from the current user's cart
### Items are automatically grouped by seller into separate seller orders
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### List Customer Orders
### Returns all orders for the authenticated customer
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### Get Order by ID
### Returns a single order by its ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### List Seller Orders
### Returns all orders containing products from the authenticated seller
### Note: Must be logged in as a seller
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sellers/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
